{"TopicId":198621,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to show more than 2 Crew Portraits?","CreatedByName":"Desdenova","CreatedById":202330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T06:41:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Desdenova","CreatedById":202330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T06:41:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, in older versions of KSP, I had no problems showing 3 crew portraits in the bottom right corner of the screen (as seen in the several-years-old screenshot below). If I recall correctly, it showed 3 slots automatically (and maybe\u00A0 4? I could be wrong about that).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00229723156BC4258C58AAEF6CD4AEFF6749AC594ACD\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002260.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/579074999582912588/9723156BC4258C58AAEF6CD4AEFF6749AC594ACD/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut nowadays, I only seem to be able to show 2 crew portraits, as seen below. I can\u0027t add more portraits, as the \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button is dark-grayed out and unclickable when 2 portraits are already displayed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222A4C7CBE474E9FF1364DBC121DF1B39FE32E2E8D\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/1662355594060897845/2A4C7CBE474E9FF1364DBC121DF1B39FE32E2E8D/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried scaling down the crew portraits so there would be more room on the screen, and maybe the game would let me add more...but no such luck. If anyone knows how to add more slots, or if anyone knows of a mod that would accomplish this, I\u0027d love to hear. It just bums me out to have the command pod with 3 seats but I can only see 2 Kerbals...!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T08:02:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223891974\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221607582490\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022202330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Desdenova\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Desdenova said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t add more portraits, as the \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button is dark-grayed out\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Ein fact your \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button looks darker.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Eit never happened to me\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022add%20slot%20button.jpg?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.20\u0022 height=\u0022281\u0022 width=\u0022500\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/cj8x67pxs8cbp57/add%20slot%20button.jpg?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"king of nowhere","CreatedById":204876,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T11:32:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni have the same issue here, i also can\u0027t add a third slot\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T11:32:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt a guess, I would say that your UI scale is too large to allow a third portrait, as this would leave the nag ball with nowhere to go. Reduce the UI scale (or increase your screen resolution)\u00A0and you should be able to add more portraits.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ConArt70","CreatedById":200187,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-10T15:59:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWorking ok on xbox, i have five crew currently displayed. I think that\u0027s the most I can have though.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Desdenova","CreatedById":202330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-11T01:53:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223892021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221607599979\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt a guess, I would say that your UI scale is too large to allow a third portrait, as this would leave the nag ball with nowhere to go. Reduce the UI scale (or increase your screen resolution)\u00A0and you should be able to add more portraits.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, my UI scale is usually much smaller, I just scaled it up so the grayed-out button would be more visible. In any case, I can scale it down as small as possible and I still can\u0027t add more slots.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223891992\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221607587330\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173370\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022antipro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, antipro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Ein fact your \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button looks darker.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Eit never happened to me\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/cj8x67pxs8cbp57/add%20slot%20button.jpg?dl=1\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022add%20slot%20button.jpg?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.20\u0022 height=\u0022281\u0022 width=\u0022500\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/cj8x67pxs8cbp57/add%20slot%20button.jpg?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDarn, that\u0027s weird. I\u0027ll keep messing with settings...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-11T08:07:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you sure that you actually \u003Ci\u003Ehave\u003C/i\u003E\u00A03 Kerbals on that ship?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ConArt70","CreatedById":200187,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-11T09:02:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223892377\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221607674071\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you sure that you actually \u003Ci\u003Ehave\u003C/i\u003E\u00A03 Kerbals on that ship?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou asked what we were all thinking!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be fair, it doesn\u0027t even look greyed out to me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Desdenova","CreatedById":202330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-12T03:23:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223892377\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221607674071\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you sure that you actually \u003Ci\u003Ehave\u003C/i\u003E\u00A03 Kerbals on that ship?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair question! This should convince you: I have the interior overlay enabled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the first pic, you can see that I have one slot shown, and when I mouse-over the \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button, the text appears as expected.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022aqzoqDu.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/aqzoqDu.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen clicked, the next slot appears. When I mouse-over the \u0022Add Slot\u0022 button now, the \u0022Add Slot\u0022 text no longer shows up to the left of the button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022GlEgMdJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/GlEgMdJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Desdenova","CreatedById":202330,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-12T03:48:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlright, I believe I\u0027ve figured it out. It seems to depend on the resolution of the screen, which is set in the settings menu\u00A0accessed from the main menu of the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the resolution is set to 1280x720, like so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00227nerR2U.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002218.00\u0022 height=\u0022180\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/7nerR2U.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthen I can only see 2 Crew Portraits, like so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022GlEgMdJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/GlEgMdJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever....when I increase my resolution to 1600x900, like so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Deuya0C.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002214.50\u0022 height=\u0022145\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Deuya0C.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthen I can add up to 4 Crew Portraits before the game prevents me from adding more! Like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022w7Yn3Lh.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/w7Yn3Lh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd when I max it out to 1920x1080...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022N1LSUx9.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002212.00\u0022 height=\u0022120\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/N1LSUx9.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthen I can see up to 5 Crew Portraits \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VpPy4dj.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VpPy4dj.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo....yes, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199902-jimmymcgoochie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022199902\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199902-jimmymcgoochie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jimmymcgoochie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0was right when they said to increase the screen resolution, I just glossed over that bit and only read the part about changing the UI scale. Guess that\u0027s a lesson in reading comprehension for me \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-12T03:55:36Z\u0022 title=\u002212/12/2020 03:55  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 12, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Desdenova\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ECrediting @jimmymcgoochie\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}